    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>rice vinegar </strong>and<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong> and<strong> sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong> to the bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>red cabbage slaw</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>plum chutney </strong>to a separate bowl with your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and mix until combined – this is your <strong>plum sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
