            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>tofu </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Slice lengthways into 3 flat pieces per person</p><p>Add the <strong>tofu slices</strong> to a plate with your <strong>cornflour</strong> and season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Turn them a few times until all of the tofu slices are fully coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
