        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated tofu</strong> <strong>slices</strong> with your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side until crispy and golden</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
