      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Once the chips are nearly done, take the tray out the oven (cooking for 3 or more? Use a separate tray!) and add the<strong> brioche halves</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 2-3 min or until the brioche bun halves are warmed through</p>",
      "order": 6,
