      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu is crispy and golden, reduce the heat to low and add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>plum sauce </strong>(save the rest for later!) and your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min further until the tofu slices are fully coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>sticky hoisin tofu</strong></p>",
